h4. Actor:
System.

h4. Description:
Name of use case represents its functionality. System will auto generate 8 digits Reference number and will return to caller user-case.

h4. Pre-condition:
N/A.

h4. Process:
* Generate 8 digits Reference Number with following logic:

** 1st 4 digits Represents Company Code.
** Next 4 digits Represents Task ID.

h4. Post-condition:

* *Success:*
** Send 8 digits Ref number to caller user case.

* *Failure:*
** Show error message for details visit [Error Handler|common Usecases].

